FBIS3-94 "drafr040_a_94007" FBIS-AFR-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Gabon Opposition Says Abessole Living With Family AB2602132094 Libreville RTG Chaine Nationale Radio Network in French 1200 GMT 26 Feb 94 AB2602132094 Libreville RTG Chaine Nationale Radio Network in French 1200 GMT 26 Feb 94 Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] A press statement just in from the National Lumberjacks Rally says the leader of that party, Father Paul Mba Abessole, is still living with his family and several militants met him. Next week, he will give a news conference to restore the truth, nothing but the truth of the facts and to propose political solutions to the current crisis. The venue and time will be made known later.
